reviewText: I was so happy to find this DVD.  It arrived quickly and looks brand new.  I will enjoy it and share it as well.

Although the disks and packaging received are in good shape, the product is not quiet what I expected.  The 2004 conference set should have included multiple DVDs with material from all the speakers at the 2004 event, not just the one featuring Luci Swindoll.  Oh well.  The one is good, but expected the complete set.  In the future the seller might want to indicate that it is a partial set.
